4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program provides a comprehensive foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Participants will learn about data loss prevention and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. The bootcamp spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes weekly for a maximum of 16 students. An official completion certificate is awarded. Courses are available in English and Spanish. 

